('https://www.phonearena.com/news/Samsung-phones-on-Oreo-will-give-descriptive-file-names-to-screenshots_id100868', '2017-12-19 11:51:00', '<img src="https://i-cdn.phonearena.com/images/article/100868-thumb/Samsung-phones-on-Oreo-will-give-descriptive-file-names-to-screenshots.jpg" alt="" hspace="5" vspace="2" align="left" /><div>If you are anything remotely like us, you have folders upon folders filled to the brim with screenshots that', 'Samsung phones on Oreo will give descriptive file names to screenshots', 'https://www.phonearena.com/news/Samsung-phones-on-Oreo-will-give-descriptive-file-names-to-screenshots_id100868', 'https://www.phonearena.com/feed/news'),
