('https://www.phonearena.com/news/The-iPhone-X-inventory-increase-could-result-in-a-T-Mobile-BOGO-deal_id100875', '2017-12-19 11:48:00', '<img src="https://i-cdn.phonearena.com/images/article/100875-thumb/The-iPhone-X-inventory-increase-could-result-in-a-T-Mobile-BOGO-deal.jpg" alt="" hspace="5" vspace="2" align="left" />Packaged with the good news that Apple is now shipping&nbsp;iPhone X units for the next business day is the bad news that this would also mean inventory increase that carriers will have to deal with. Wells Fargo analysts are at the opinion that sooner or later this would lead to what seemed impossible just a week ago - an iPhone X BOGO.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div>Yes, if history is any indication, they place their bets on the shoot-from-the-hip T-Mobile to get aggressive with post-holiday promos, and launch an iPhone X twofer campaign that is sure to shake up the promo field. Verizon already launched ...', 'The iPhone X inventory increase could result in a T-Mobile BOGO deal', 'https://www.phonearena.com/news/The-iPhone-X-inventory-increase-could-result-in-a-T-Mobile-BOGO-deal_id100875', 'https://www.phonearena.com/feed/news'),
('https://www.phonearena.com/news/These-10-paid-Android-games-are-now-free-for-a-limited-time-grab-them-while-you-can_id100881', '2017-12-19 16:14:00', '<img src="https://i-cdn.phonearena.com/images/article/100881-thumb/These-10-paid-Android-games-are-now-free-for-a-limited-time-grab-them-while-you-can.jpg" alt="" hspace="5" vspace="2" align="left" /><div></div><div><br></div>Looking for some neat new games to play on your Android smartphone? If that\'s the case, you might be pleased to hear that several titles that are usually paid are now available for free on Google Play.<br><br>This collection features several different genres, so we\'ve made sure to include a video (where available) or gameplay image and a description below each title in order to aid you in the selection process.<br><br>Also, make sure to check out the end of sale times for each game below the respective download link. At the time of writing (December 19th), some of these ...', 'These 10 paid Android games are now free for a limited time, grab them while you can!', 'https://www.phonearena.com/news/These-10-paid-Android-games-are-now-free-for-a-limited-time-grab-them-while-you-can_id100881', 'https://www.phonearena.com/feed/news'),
('https://www.phonearena.com/news/This-is-where-the-Galaxy-S9-fingerprint-scanner-goes_id100877', '2017-12-19 12:23:00', '<img src="https://i-cdn.phonearena.com/images/article/100877-thumb/This-is-where-the-Galaxy-S9-fingerprint-scanner-goes.jpg" alt="" hspace="5" vspace="2" align="left" />Samsung just unveiled its 2018 midrangers, the Galaxy A8 and A8+, and, buried in specs and size comparisons, as well as chomping on', 'This is where the Galaxy S9 fingerprint scanner goes', 'https://www.phonearena.com/news/This-is-where-the-Galaxy-S9-fingerprint-scanner-goes_id100877', 'https://www.phonearena.com/feed/news'),
('https://www.phonearena.com/news/Today-only-save-200-on-select-Apple-Watch-Series-2-models-at-Best-Buy_id100847', '2017-12-18 21:21:00', '<img src="https://i-cdn.phonearena.com/images/article/100847-thumb/Today-only-save-200-on-select-Apple-Watch-Series-2-models-at-Best-Buy.jpg" alt="" hspace="5" vspace="2" align="left" />When Apple unveiled the Apple Watch Series 3 in September, it closed the book on the Series 2. This left the Series 1 for budget minded consumers, and Series 3 for those who love spending money on the latest tech items. But this left big box retailer Best Buy with a large inventory of Series 2 timepieces that it is trying to reduce with a $200 sale on several models. The discounted pricing is available for today only, inside Best Buy stores as a Doorbuster special. Seven different models are getting the $200 price cut. <br><br>The cheapest two models are priced at $349 and come with a "Sport" band ...', 'Today only, save $200 on select Apple Watch Series 2 models at Best Buy', 'https://www.phonearena.com/news/Today-only-save-200-on-select-Apple-Watch-Series-2-models-at-Best-Buy_id100847', 'https://www.phonearena.com/feed/news'),
('https://www.phonearena.com/news/Upcoming-Nokia-9-Avatar-will-feature-Android-Oreo-3250-mAh-battery-no-Snapdragon-845_id100893', '2017-12-19 20:18:00', '<img src="https://i-cdn.phonearena.com/images/article/100893-thumb/Upcoming-Nokia-9-Avatar-will-feature-Android-Oreo-3250-mAh-battery-no-Snapdragon-845.jpg" alt="" hspace="5" vspace="2" align="left" /><br>After launching the Nokia 8 (in select markets only), HMD\nGlobal - the new home of Nokia smartphones - is now getting ready to unveil another\nhigh-end handset, most likely called Nokia 9.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nEarlier this month, we heard that the Nokia 9 could be\nofficially announced in January, thus in about a month\'s time. Now, we have new\ndetails regarding the smartphone, as the device has been approved by the US\nFederal Communications Commission (FCC).\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAccording to documents found at the FCC, the new Nokia\nphone, model number TA-1005, is codenamed Avatar. The handset runs Android 8\nOreo, sports ...', 'Upcoming Nokia 9 (Avatar) will feature Android Oreo, 3250 mAh battery, no Snapdragon 845', 'https://www.phonearena.com/news/Upcoming-Nokia-9-Avatar-will-feature-Android-Oreo-3250-mAh-battery-no-Snapdragon-845_id100893', 'https://www.phonearena.com/feed/news');
